graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebook Workbench Images<br/>Component]

    %% External Base Dependencies (Required)
    Notebooks -->|base OS| UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.9<br/>registry.access.redhat.com]
    Notebooks -->|base OS| UBI8[UBI8 Python 3.8<br/>registry.access.redhat.com]
    Notebooks -->|notebook IDE| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 3.2-3.6]
    Notebooks -->|classic notebook| NotebookPkg[Notebook 6.4-6.5]
    Notebooks -->|cluster CLI| OC[OpenShift CLI oc<br/>stable]

    %% Framework Dependencies (Optional - Specialized Images)
    Notebooks -.->|ML framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x]
    Notebooks -.->|ML framework| PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x]
    Notebooks -.->|GPU acceleration| CUDA[CUDA Toolkit 11.x-12.x<br/>NVIDIA]
    Notebooks -.->|Intel GPU| IntelTF[Intel Extension for TensorFlow]
    Notebooks -.->|Intel GPU| IntelPT[Intel Extension for PyTorch]
    Notebooks -.->|Habana Gaudi| Habana[SynapseAI SDK 1.9-1.13<br/>DEACTIVATED in 2.10]
    Notebooks -.->|IDE| CodeServer[Code Server 4.x]
    Notebooks -.->|R IDE| RStudio[RStudio Server 4.3]
    Notebooks -.->|pipelines| Elyra[Elyra 3.x<br/>Runtime Images]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies (Consumed By)
    NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller] -->|creates StatefulSets using| Notebooks
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -->|presents ImageStreams to users| Notebooks
    JupyterHub[JupyterHub] -.->|optional spawner| Notebooks
    KFP[Kubeflow Pipelines] -->|executes runtime images| Notebooks
    ServiceMesh[Service Mesh] -.->|sidecar injection| Notebooks

    %% Integration Points (Data Flow)
    Notebooks -.->|trains models for| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    Notebooks -->|reads/writes data| S3[S3 Object Storage<br/>Minio/AWS]

    %% External Services (Runtime)
    Notebooks -->|API calls| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]
    Notebooks -->|pip install| PyPI[PyPI/Conda Repos<br/>443/TCP]
    Notebooks -->|git clone| GitHub[GitHub/GitLab<br/>443/TCP]
    Notebooks -->|image distribution| QuayIO[Quay.io Registry<br/>quay.io/modh]

    %% Styling - Component
    style Notebooks fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

    %% Styling - External Dependencies (Required)
    style UBI9 fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style UBI8 fill:#ee0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff
    style JupyterLab fill:#f37726,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookPkg fill:#f37726,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OC fill:#cc0000,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff

    %% Styling - Framework Dependencies (Optional)
    style TensorFlow fill:#ff6f00,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style PyTorch fill:#ee4c2c,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style CUDA fill:#76b900,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style IntelTF fill:#0071c5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff
    style IntelPT fill:#0071c5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff
    style Habana fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style CodeServer fill:#007acc,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff
    style RStudio fill:#75aadb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style Elyra fill:#9013fe,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px,color:#fff

    %% Styling - Internal ODH (Green)
    style NotebookController fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style JupyterHub fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style KFP fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style ModelRegistry fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px

    %% Styling - External Services (Gray)
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style K8sAPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style PyPI fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style GitHub fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style QuayIO fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    %% Legend
    subgraph Legend[" "]
        direction TB
        L1[" Solid line = Required dependency "]
        L2[" Dashed line = Optional/Conditional "]
        L3[" "]
    end

    style Legend fill:#ffffff,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    style L1 fill:#ffffff,stroke:none
    style L2 fill:#ffffff,stroke:none
    style L3 fill:#ffffff,stroke:none
